reviewText: If your child likes history or is interested in inventions they will love this. Great gift.

I purchased this to show my high school students, but ultimately have not. Much of the video is old movie/ad clips, with the Dyson thrown in for modernization. Picture an instructional movie from the 1960's and there you have it. The one thing I that made me smile were the sections on making a woman's life in the home easier...hooray for the electric washing machine!
